<h2>如果意译外国人的名字会怎么样?</h2><div><div>
<img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-f7ed7540dbd7bebc42e8d55de18fe514_l.jpg?source=8673f162">
<span>ICARUS，</span><span>职业仙子</span>
<a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/418150145/answer/1440420905" hidden>阅读原文</a>
</div><div>
<p>意大利部分姓氏会很惨烈。</p><p>Bevilacqua 您喝水</p><p>Passalacqua 递水</p><p>Lacavalla 母马</p><p>Maiale 猪</p><p>Sesso 性</p><p>Gonfiacani 吹小狗</p><p>Mangiacapre 吃羊</p><p>Cecagallina 瞎鸡</p><p>Bastardo 王 8 蛋</p><p>Pipi 嘘嘘（液体）</p><p>还有更多</p><p><a href="http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.cognomix.it/cognomi-strani-divertenti-ridicoli-imbarazzanti.php" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Cognomi Strani, Buffi, Ridicoli e Divertenti dall'Elenco Telefonico</a></p><p>直接点翻译就可以看了，简直灾难。</p>
